00276                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00277      IF WS-RESULT-DA     GREATER THAN +0  OR                      ELCRTMPD
00278         TERM-IN-MONTHS    GREATER THAN +0                         ELCRTMPD
00279          COMPUTE CP-REMAINING-TERM-1 =                            ELCRTMPD
00280                              CP-REMAINING-TERM-1 - (+1).          ELCRTMPD
00281                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00282      GO TO 199-END-CERT-DATE-PROCESSING.                          ELCRTMPD
00283                                                                   ELCRTMPD
