00371                                                                      CL**5
00372 ****************************************************************  ELCRTMPD
00373 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00374 *  PROCESSING FOR VALUATION DATE ON OR AFTER 1ST PAYMENT DATE  *  ELCRTMPD
00375 *  AND CONSIDERING EXTENSION DAYS.                             *  ELCRTMPD
00376 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00377 ****************************************************************  ELCRTMPD
00378                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00379  200-PROCESS-WITH-1ST-PMT-DATE.                                   ELCRTMPD
00380                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00381 ****************************************************************  ELCRTMPD
00382 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00383 *  COMPUTE AN EXPIRATION DATE USING THE 1ST PAYMENT DATE  AND  *  ELCRTMPD
00384 *  THE (REMAINING TERM - 1). IF THE VALUATION DATE IS GREATER  *  ELCRTMPD
00385 *  THAN THIS ESTIMATED DATE, THEN THE TERM IS CONSIDERED TO    *  ELCRTMPD
00386 *  BE FULLY EXPIRED.                                           *  ELCRTMPD
00387 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00388 ****************************************************************  ELCRTMPD
00389                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00390      MOVE CP-FIRST-PAY-DATE      TO DC-BIN-DATE-1.                ELCRTMPD
00391                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00392      COMPUTE DC-ELAPSED-MONTHS EQUAL                              ELCRTMPD
00393          (CP-ORIGINAL-TERM - +1).                                 ELCRTMPD
00394                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00395      MOVE ZEROS                  TO DC-ELAPSED-DAYS.              ELCRTMPD
00396      MOVE '6'                    TO DC-OPTION-CODE.               ELCRTMPD
00397      PERFORM 8000-DATE-CONVERT THRU 8000-EXIT.                    ELCRTMPD
00398                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00399      IF DATE-CONVERSION-ERROR                                     ELCRTMPD
00400         MOVE '2' TO CP-RETURN-CODE                                ELCRTMPD
00401         GO TO 9999-RT-REMAINING-TERM-XIT                          ELCRTMPD
00402      ELSE                                                         ELCRTMPD
00403         IF DC-BIN-DATE-2 NOT GREATER CP-VALUATION-DT              ELCRTMPD
00404             MOVE ZEROS TO CP-REMAINING-TERM-1                     ELCRTMPD
00405                           CP-REMAINING-TERM-2                     ELCRTMPD
00406                           CP-REMAINING-TERM-3                     ELCRTMPD
00407             GO TO 9999-RT-REMAINING-TERM-XIT.                     ELCRTMPD
00408                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00409                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00410  EJECT                                                            ELCRTMPD
00411 ****************************************************************  ELCRTMPD
00412 *  REMAINING-TERM-2 REFLECTS THE NUMBER OF PAYMENTS THAT A     *  ELCRTMPD
00413 *  INSURED HAS LEFT TO PAY. REQUARDLESS OF THE AMOUNT OF TIME  *  ELCRTMPD
00414 *  THAT HAS ELAPSED FROM THE EFFECTIVE DATE TO THE FIRST       *  ELCRTMPD
00415 *  PAYMENT DATE, ONLY ONE MONTH IS EARNED.  THE NUMBER OF      *  ELCRTMPD
00416 *  PAYMENTS IS THEN EVALUATED FROM THE FIRST PAYMENT DATE TO   *  ELCRTMPD
00417 *  THE VALUATION DATE.                                         *  ELCRTMPD
00418 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00419 *  IF THE VALUATION DATE IS GREATER THAN THE 1ST PAYMENT       *  ELCRTMPD
00420 *  DATE, ONE MONTH HAS BEEN EARNED FOR REMAINING TERM-2.       *  ELCRTMPD
00421 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00422 *   NOTE : THE MAXIMUM MONTHS EARNED FORM THE EFFECTIVE DATE   *  ELCRTMPD
00423 *     TO THE PAYMENT DATE IS 1.                                *  ELCRTMPD
00424 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00425 ****************************************************************  ELCRTMPD
00426                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00427      IF CP-VALUATION-DT NOT LESS THAN CP-FIRST-PAY-DATE           ELCRTMPD
00428          MOVE 1                  TO MONTHS-EARNED-2               ELCRTMPD
00429      ELSE                                                         ELCRTMPD
00430          MOVE 0                  TO MONTHS-EARNED-2.              ELCRTMPD
00431                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00432      MOVE WS-SAVE-VALUATION-DATE TO WS-TOP-NUMBER.                ELCRTMPD
00433      MOVE CP-VALUATION-DT        TO WS-SAVE-BINARY-DATE.          ELCRTMPD
00434                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00435      MOVE WS-SAVE-PAYMENT-DATE   TO WS-BOTTOM-NUMBER.             ELCRTMPD
00436                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00437      PERFORM 500-SIMPLE-ARITHMETIC THRU 500-EXIT.                 ELCRTMPD
00438                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00439      COMPUTE CP-REMAINING-TERM-2 = CP-ORIGINAL-TERM -             ELCRTMPD
00440                           (TERM-IN-MONTHS  + MONTHS-EARNED-2).    ELCRTMPD
00441                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00442      IF CP-REMAINING-TERM-2 NEGATIVE                              ELCRTMPD
00443         MOVE 0                   TO CP-REMAINING-TERM-1           ELCRTMPD
00444                                     CP-REMAINING-TERM-2           ELCRTMPD
00445                                     CP-REMAINING-TERM-3           ELCRTMPD
00446                                     CP-ODD-DAYS                   ELCRTMPD
00447         GO TO 9999-RT-REMAINING-TERM-XIT.                         ELCRTMPD
00448                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00449      MOVE CP-REMAINING-TERM-2    TO CP-REMAINING-TERM-3.          ELCRTMPD
00450                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00451      IF CP-EARN-AS-REG-BALLOON                                    ELCRTMPD
00452         IF CP-BALLOON-LAST-PMT                                    ELCRTMPD
00453            ADD +1 TO CP-REMAINING-TERM-3.                         ELCRTMPD
00454                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00455      IF CP-EARN-ON-FULL-MONTH                                     ELCRTMPD
00456         MOVE CP-REMAINING-TERM-2    TO CP-REMAINING-TERM-1        ELCRTMPD
00457         MOVE 0                      TO CP-ODD-DAYS                ELCRTMPD
00458         GO TO 9999-RT-REMAINING-TERM-XIT.                         ELCRTMPD
00459                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00460                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00461  EJECT                                                            ELCRTMPD
00462 ****************************************************************  ELCRTMPD
00463 *  REMAINING-TERM-1 IS USED FOR REFUNDS ETC.  THE TERM IS      *  ELCRTMPD
00464 *  CALCULATED FROM THE FIRST PAYMENT DATE TO THE VALUATION     *  ELCRTMPD
00465 *  DATE EARNING NO MORE THAN ONE MONTH FROM EFFECTIVE DATE TO  *  ELCRTMPD
00466 *  1ST PAYMENT DATE.                                           *  ELCRTMPD
00467 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00468 *  THE TIME ELAPSED FROM THE EFFECTIVE DATE AND THE FIRST      *  ELCRTMPD
00469 *  PAYMENT DATE MUST BE 1 MONTH BEFORE IT IS CONSIDERED        *  ELCRTMPD
00470 *  EARNED.                                                     *  ELCRTMPD
00471 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00472 *   NOTE : THE MAXIMUM MONTHS EARNED FORM THE EFFECTIVE DATE   *  ELCRTMPD
00473 *     TO THE PAYMENT DATE IS 1.                                *  ELCRTMPD
00474 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00475 ****************************************************************  ELCRTMPD
00476                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00477      MOVE WS-SAVE-PAYMENT-DATE   TO WS-TOP-NUMBER.                ELCRTMPD
00478      MOVE CP-FIRST-PAY-DATE      TO WS-SAVE-BINARY-DATE.          ELCRTMPD
00479                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00480      MOVE WS-SAVE-EFFECTIVE-DATE TO WS-BOTTOM-NUMBER.             ELCRTMPD
00481                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00482      IF PAYMENT-DATE-EOM AND EFFECTIVE-DATE-EOM                   ELCRTMPD
00483          MOVE ZEROS              TO WS-TOP-DA                     ELCRTMPD
00484                                     WS-BOTTOM-DA.                 ELCRTMPD
00485                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00486      PERFORM 500-SIMPLE-ARITHMETIC THRU 500-EXIT.                 ELCRTMPD
00487                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00488      MOVE ZERO                   TO MONTHS-EARNED-1.              ELCRTMPD
00489                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00490      IF TERM-IN-MONTHS  GREATER THAN +0                           ELCRTMPD
00491          MOVE 1                    TO MONTHS-EARNED-1             ELCRTMPD
00492          MOVE WS-SAVE-PAYMENT-DATE TO WS-BOTTOM-NUMBER            ELCRTMPD
00493          GO TO 205-1ST-PAY-TO-VALUATION-DATE                      ELCRTMPD
00494      ELSE                                                         ELCRTMPD
00495          MOVE WS-SAVE-EFFECTIVE-DATE TO WS-BOTTOM-NUMBER          ELCRTMPD
00496          GO TO 205-1ST-PAY-TO-VALUATION-DATE.                     ELCRTMPD
00497                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00498  EJECT                                                            ELCRTMPD
00499 ****************************************************************  ELCRTMPD
00500 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00501 *  COMPUTE THE ELAPSED TIME BETWEEN THE 1ST PAYMENT DATE       *  ELCRTMPD
00502 *  AND THE VALUATION/CANCEL DATE.                              *  ELCRTMPD
00503 *   THE REMAINING TERM THEN BECOMES :                          *  ELCRTMPD
00504 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00505 *  ORIGINAL TERM - (CALCULATED ELAPSED MONTHS + MONTHS EARNED) *  ELCRTMPD
00506 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00507 ****************************************************************  ELCRTMPD
00508                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00509  205-1ST-PAY-TO-VALUATION-DATE.                                   ELCRTMPD
00510                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00511      MOVE WS-SAVE-VALUATION-DATE TO WS-TOP-NUMBER.                ELCRTMPD
00512      MOVE CP-VALUATION-DT        TO WS-SAVE-BINARY-DATE.          ELCRTMPD
00513                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00514      PERFORM 500-SIMPLE-ARITHMETIC THRU 500-EXIT.                 ELCRTMPD
00515                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00516      MOVE WS-RESULT-DA           TO CP-ODD-DAYS.                  ELCRTMPD
00517                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00518      COMPUTE CP-REMAINING-TERM-1 = CP-ORIGINAL-TERM -             ELCRTMPD
00519                           (TERM-IN-MONTHS  + MONTHS-EARNED-1).    ELCRTMPD
00520                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00521  EJECT                                                            ELCRTMPD
00522 ****************************************************************  ELCRTMPD
00523 * IF THIS TERM IS NEGATIVE, THE TERM IS CONSIDERED TO BE       *  ELCRTMPD
00524 *  EXPIRED AND ALL PREMIUM IS EARNED.                          *  ELCRTMPD
00525 ****************************************************************  ELCRTMPD
00526      IF CP-REMAINING-TERM-1 NEGATIVE                              ELCRTMPD
00527         MOVE ZERO                TO CP-REMAINING-TERM-1           ELCRTMPD
00528                                     CP-ODD-DAYS                   ELCRTMPD
00529         GO TO 9999-RT-REMAINING-TERM-XIT.                         ELCRTMPD
00530                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00531      IF CP-EARN-AFTER-15TH                                        ELCRTMPD
00532         GO TO 410-METHOD-1.                                       ELCRTMPD
00533      IF CP-EARN-ON-HALF-MONTH                                     ELCRTMPD
00534         GO TO 420-METHOD-2.                                       ELCRTMPD
00535      IF CP-EARN-ON-1ST-DAY                                        ELCRTMPD
00536         GO TO 430-METHOD-3.                                       ELCRTMPD
00537      IF CP-EARN-ON-FULL-MONTH                                     ELCRTMPD
00538         GO TO 440-METHOD-4.                                       ELCRTMPD
00539      IF CP-EARN-WITH-NO-DAYS                                      ELCRTMPD
00540         GO TO 450-METHOD-5.                                       ELCRTMPD
00541      IF CP-EARN-AFTER-14TH                                        ELCRTMPD
00542         GO TO 460-METHOD-6.                                       ELCRTMPD
00543      IF CP-EARN-AFTER-16TH                                        ELCRTMPD
00544         GO TO 470-METHOD-7.                                       ELCRTMPD
00545                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00546                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00547 ****************************************************************  ELCRTMPD
00548 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00549 *   IF NONE OF THE ABOVE OPTIONS HAVE BEEN SPECIFIED, THEN     *  ELCRTMPD
00550 *   INDICATE THERE WAS AN ERROR IN THE OPTION SELECTION AND    *  ELCRTMPD
00551 *   EXIT FROM THE ROUTINE.                                     *  ELCRTMPD
00552 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00553 ****************************************************************  ELCRTMPD
00554                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00555      MOVE '3' TO CP-RETURN-CODE                                   ELCRTMPD
00556      GO TO 9999-RT-REMAINING-TERM-XIT.                            ELCRTMPD
00557                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00558  EJECT                                                            ELCRTMPD
00559 ****************************************************************  ELCRTMPD
00560 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00561 *  PROCESSING FOR VALUATION DATE AFTER THE CERT-EFFECTIVE DATE *  ELCRTMPD
00562 *  NOT CONSIDERING EXTENSION DAYS.                             *  ELCRTMPD
00563 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00564 ****************************************************************  ELCRTMPD
00565                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00566  300-PROCESS-WITH-CERT-EFF-DATE.                                  ELCRTMPD
00567                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00568 ****************************************************************  ELCRTMPD
00569 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00570 *  COMPUTE AN EXPIRATION DATE USING THE CERTIFICATE EFFECTIVE  *  ELCRTMPD
00571 *  DATE AND ORIGINAL TERM. IF THE CANCEL DATE IS GREATER THAN  *  ELCRTMPD
00572 *  THIS ESTIMATED DATE, THEN THE TERM IS CONSIDERED TO BE FULLY*  ELCRTMPD
00573 *  EXHAUSTED.                                                  *  ELCRTMPD
00574 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00575 ****************************************************************  ELCRTMPD
00576                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00577      MOVE CP-CERT-EFF-DT         TO DC-BIN-DATE-1.                ELCRTMPD
00578      MOVE CP-ORIGINAL-TERM       TO DC-ELAPSED-MONTHS.            ELCRTMPD
00579      MOVE ZEROS                  TO DC-ELAPSED-DAYS.              ELCRTMPD
00580      MOVE '6'                    TO DC-OPTION-CODE.               ELCRTMPD
00581      PERFORM 8000-DATE-CONVERT THRU 8000-EXIT.                    ELCRTMPD
00582                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00583      IF DATE-CONVERSION-ERROR                                     ELCRTMPD
00584         MOVE '2' TO CP-RETURN-CODE                                ELCRTMPD
00585         GO TO 9999-RT-REMAINING-TERM-XIT                          ELCRTMPD
00586      ELSE                                                         ELCRTMPD
00587         IF DC-BIN-DATE-2 LESS THAN CP-VALUATION-DT                ELCRTMPD
00588             MOVE ZEROS TO CP-REMAINING-TERM-1                     ELCRTMPD
00589                           CP-REMAINING-TERM-2                     ELCRTMPD
00590                           CP-REMAINING-TERM-3                     ELCRTMPD
00591             GO TO 9999-RT-REMAINING-TERM-XIT.                     ELCRTMPD
00592  EJECT                                                            ELCRTMPD
00593 ****************************************************************  ELCRTMPD
00594 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00595 *  COMPUTE THE ELAPSED TIME BETWEEN THE EFFECTIVE DATE         *  ELCRTMPD
00596 *  AND THE CANCEL DATE.                                        *  ELCRTMPD
00597 *                                                              *  ELCRTMPD
00598 ****************************************************************  ELCRTMPD
00599                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00600  305-EFF-TO-VALUATION-DATE.                                       ELCRTMPD
00601                                                                   ELCRTMPD
