00640         GO TO 420-METHOD-2.                                       ELCRTMPD
00641      IF CP-EARN-ON-1ST-DAY                                        ELCRTMPD
00642         GO TO 430-METHOD-3.                                       ELCRTMPD
00643      IF CP-EARN-ON-FULL-MONTH                                     ELCRTMPD
00644         GO TO 440-METHOD-4.                                       ELCRTMPD
00645      IF CP-EARN-WITH-NO-DAYS                                      ELCRTMPD
00646         GO TO 450-METHOD-5.                                       ELCRTMPD
00647      IF CP-EARN-AFTER-14TH                                        ELCRTMPD
00648         GO TO 460-METHOD-6.                                       ELCRTMPD
00649      IF CP-EARN-AFTER-16TH                                        ELCRTMPD
00650         GO TO 470-METHOD-7.                                       ELCRTMPD
00651                                                                   ELCRTMPD
