00973          COMPUTE CP-REMAINING-TERM-1 =                            ELCRTMPD
00974                              CP-REMAINING-TERM-1 + (+1).          ELCRTMPD
00975                                                                   ELCRTMPD
00976      GO TO 680-END-NCL-PROCESSING.                                ELCRTMPD
